<section id="To_add_a_Customization_Template3" remap="TID_15518">
	<title>Adding a Customization Template</title>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Add a Customization Template</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Infrastructure</guimenu><guisubmenu>PXE</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the <guilabel>Customization Templates</guilabel> accordion.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1847.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject><guilabel>(Configuration)</guilabel>, 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/1848.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject><guilabel>(Add a new Customization Template)</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				In <guilabel>Basic Information</guilabel>, type in a <guilabel>Name</guilabel> and <guilabel>Description</guilabel>.
			</para>
			<mediaobject>
				<imageobject>
					<imagedata align="center" fileref="images/2324.png" />
				</imageobject>
			</mediaobject>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Select the <guilabel>Image Type</guilabel>. This list should include the PXE image types you created.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				In <guilabel>Type</guilabel>, select <guimenuitem>Kickstart</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>CloudInit</guimenuitem> for Linux based systems, and <guimenuitem>Sysprep</guimenuitem> for Windows based system.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				In the <guimenuitem>Script</guimenuitem> area, either paste the script from another source or type the script directly into the <productname>CloudForms Management Engine</productname> interface.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click <guibutton>Add</guibutton>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
	<note>
		<para>
			The default dialogs show all possible parameters for provisioning. To limit the options shown, see <xref linkend="sect-Customizing_Provisioning_Dialogs" />.
		</para>
	</note>
</section>